metadata.name: Free Will
metadata.description:
The notion of FREE WILL used to be a widespread and welcomed within past decade.

Sam Harris claims that our so called free will is predetermined by our personality and psychology. Daniel Kahneman proved that people tend to adjust their decisions accordingly to group.

Today the question ‘whether free will really exists and what it is’ is highly disturbing. Free will not to do violence. Free will to speak out and name black as black and white as white. When ones deprived of speaking how can others know?
